{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1cb178ad1d","title":"致彭德怀等电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ad01aac6e8","index":0,"year":1947,"month":8,"day":12,"articleId":"1cb178ad1d"}],"tags":[{"id":"ae0a6697a5","name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"d0a2337495","name":"贺龙","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji23","name":"毛泽东全集第23卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji23.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji23":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3cb5232cb4","type":"paragraph","text":"致彭德怀等电”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"1cb178ad1d"},{"id":"970a1bacce","type":"paragraph","text":"（1947年8月12日）（一）我攻榆林未克，敌钟松巴部明元日可进榆林，刘五个旅可到麟镇以东。（二）我军即在榆林、米脂间休整待机，隔断刘、钟两部，吸引该敌，以利陈、谢行动。陈、谢定于未贺渡河。（三）为防刘、童进占绥德，我无定河、黄河间各后方机关，必须迅速移至黄河以东，望贺、习立即部署移动L这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的致彭德怀，贺龙、习仲融电的主要内容。这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的致彭德怀，贺龙、习仲融电的主[2]钟松，当时任国民党军整续第三十六师师长。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"1cb178ad1d"}],"page":{"id":"7f976ca404","publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"1cb178ad1d","start":205,"end":205}}}},"__N_SSG":true}